window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Three lives come together in a story of love, loss, and second chances.</p> <p>Smriti, a single mother to Jia, has always put duty before everything else. When she meets Keshav at a support group, her world starts to feel lighter. For the first time in years, she allows herself to hope for happiness.</p> <p>But just as life seems to be falling into place, a call from Jia's boarding school changes everything. One tragedy leads to another, and soon, Jia is left with nothing. As grief and uncertainty take over, Smriti and Keshav must find a way to hold on to each other and to the family they never expected to build. In the end, family isn't just about blood-it's about the people who choose to stay.</p>"; 
